  - 通过数轴可视化有理数 / Visualize rational numbers through number lines
  - 逐步引入抽象概念 / Gradually introduce abstract concepts

### 4.3 形式运算阶段（12+岁）/ Formal Operational Stage (12+ years)

**有理数在形式运算阶段的理解 / Understanding Rational Numbers in the Formal Operational Stage**：

- **抽象思维 / Abstract Thinking**：
