|------|-----------|-----------|
| **Tall感知-操作世界 / Tall Embodied World** | 数数和计数 / Counting and enumeration | 分割和测量 / Division and measurement |
| **Tall概念-符号世界 / Tall Symbolic World** | 数字符号和运算 / Number notation and operations | 分数符号和小数符号 / Fraction notation and decimal notation |
| **Tall形式-公理世界 / Tall Formal World** | Peano公理系统 / Peano axiom system | 有理数域公理系统 / Rational number field axiom system |
| **APOS Action** | 数数和计数操作 / Counting and enumeration operations | 分割和测量操作 / Division and measurement operations |
| **APOS Process** | 自然数运算过程 / Natural number operation process | 有理数运算过程 / Rational number operation process |
| **APOS Object** | 自然数的集合 / Set of natural numbers | 有理数的域 / Field of rational numbers |
| **APOS Schema** | 自然数概念图式 / Natural number concept schema | 有理数概念图式 / Rational number concept schema |
| **Piaget阶段 / Piaget Stage** | 具体运算阶段 / Concrete operational stage | 前运算、具体运算、形式运算阶段 / Pre-operational, concrete operational, formal operational stages |

**关键差异 / Key Differences**：

- 自然数更强调"计数"和"顺序" / Natural numbers emphasize "counting" and "order" more
- 有理数更强调"分割"、"比例"和"测量" / Rational numbers emphasize "division", "proportion", and "measurement" more
- 有理数需要理解分数概念，这是自然数概念的扩展 / Rational numbers require understanding fraction concepts, which is an extension of natural number concepts

